# --- Build graph scope ("how the website is built") ---
# This .graphifyignore governs the ROOT graph in graphify-out/, which is scoped to
# the site machinery: layouts, theme, assets, config, deploy. The prose in content/
# is a SEPARATE graph in content-graph/graphify-out/ (built/updated on its own).
# Keep both excluded here so a root rebuild never ingests content or the content graph.
content/
content-graph/
static/js/
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.webp
*.ico
*.avif
*.bmp
*.tiff
